== Rice Panicle Segmentation
We have developed a Gaussian mixture model based unsupervised image segmentation algorithm that can segment rice panicles. The proposed method outperforms existing methods like [https://plantmethods.biomedcentral.com/articles/10.1186/s13007-017-0254-7 Panicle-SEG] with an average F1 score greater than 80%. 
- ``Unsupervised Bayesian Learning for Rice Panicle Segmentation with UAV Images,''- \[*Under Review*] \[[https://github.com/mahayat/UBLRPSUI GitHub]] 
